dictionary.description: The Mystical Fox on the world of Ohbanahara. Legends and fairytales tell that it came to exist long before humanity as a divine beast and protector of the land. It holds the power to see into the hearts of humans, and has granted many blessings on good-natured individuals in the past. However, tales also hold that it levies fearsome punishments against those with impure hearts. As a mirror for human hearts, it has long been a source of fear and awe for many people.
dictionary.evolution:
A good effort.
So long as you follow the path of the righteous, I will aid you on your way.
dictionary.fusion:
I am the looking glass.
If you ask of me, I must answer...
dictionary.summon: Changing your appearance will never deceive me. That is the way of the world.
